               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few lines on the incipit page of Text I and Text II, alternating with black lines; titles of books to be read; a few lines on the incipit page of 1 Corinthians 15 (fol. 25r); abbreviation of yǝbǝl kahǝn nǝfq (fol. 29r); elements of the punctuation signs and text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals in Text I; the word barǝkännä (fols. 3vab, 4ra).</rubric>
